{"lastModified":1773089667986,"uri":"c::7580644139::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nCALM DOWN is a 30.00m / 99ft Motor Superyacht built in 2023 by Fethiye Shipyard. Sleeping 12 guests in 6 cabins and with a crew of 7. Cruising at 12.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 14.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprises 3 master suites, two double cabins and one twin cabin.","blueprint":{"name":"CALM DOWN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c743dbf0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c744c650-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7449f40-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7433fb0-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c743b4e0-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7438dd1-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c743dbf0-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c745fed0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7469b10-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7442a10-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7475e60-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7453b80-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7464cf0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7438dd0-8d62-11f0-bad8-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7471040-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7478570-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c748e500-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c749a850-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c74a92b0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7495a30-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c747faa0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c74896e0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c7486fd0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c74a4490-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c74ab9c0-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::c749a851-8d62-11f0-bad9-7fbde39b26b2/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Fethiye Shipyard","maxCrew":7,"sleeps":12,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::b5e51bd0-8ee5-11ee-8ae2-e397792d698b","name":"Bodrum Harbour","coordinates":{"latitude":37.03328467551243,"longitude":27.42915251728127},"country":"Türkiye"},"builtYear":2023,"refitYear":"","topSpeed":14,"cruiseSpeed":12,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabins","value":"3"},{"label":"Double Cabins","value":"2"},{"label":"Twin Cabin","value":"1"}],"cabins":6,"bathrooms":6,"length":30,"beam":7,"draft":3.15,"hullType":"Semi-displacement","hullConstruction":"GRP","tonnage":190,"superStructure":["GRP"],"engines":"2 x Volvo 600 Hp","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Deck Jacuzzi"},{"label":"Outdoor Shower"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Foredeck Seating"},{"label":"Indoor Dining"},{"label":"Watermaker"},{"label":" Ice Maker"},{"label":"Washing machine"},{"label":"Full Sailing Equipments"},{"label":" Sun Mattresses"},{"label":"Life Jackets"},{"label":"Flybridge"}],"toys":[{"label":"Bathing Platform"},{"label":"Banana"},{"label":"Jet-Ski"},{"label":"Paddleboard"},{"label":"Water-Ski"},{"label":"Ringo"}],"entertainment":["Wi-Fi","Tv & Dvd In All Cabins","Card Games","Backgammon"],"tenders":["Northstar 115 HP 5.8"]},"crew":[{"name":"Serkan Akın","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::edc00ae0-8e27-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nSerkan is 42 years old and he is holding a Class Captain's Diploma (Yacht Captain). He also holds Certificates in First Aid and he is an expert in several Survival Techniques, counting many years of experience in the yachting industry. Captain Serkan will take good care of the guests, being a hardworking and responsible person. The lucky guests will surely enjoy their cruise in the hands of Cpt. Serkan , as they will visit truly amazing destinations with turquoise waters. He is very experienced one and we are very lucky that he is working with us for 3 years on the same yacht. He has 2 childs and in his free time, he likes travelling with his family. Speaks Turkish and English. \n"},{"name":"Yunus Adiyaman","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::19d54a50-8e28-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nYunus is 35 years old and he is very experienced chef on the sea , he has many luxury yachts experience in his past. He\nprepares food meticulously and hygienically from all over the world kitchens , serves them with aesthetic presentations. He is able to process and cook lobsters, scallops, oysters, other crustaceans and seafoods. Knowledgeable in HACCP Principles and Food Allergies. Holder of Food Safety Certificate, Work Safety Certificate and Hygiene Certificate. Yunus has a pleasant character with a genuine smile on his face that will make the guests feel very comfortable onboard. In his spare time, he likes watching movies and spending time with his friends. Speaks Turkish and middle level English.\n"},{"name":"Melisa Adak","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::34ff54b0-8e28-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nMelisa is 27 years old and she has been working for 6 years with the quality yachts as Hostess. She has all certificates about the seamanship and many workshops licences. She is very warm relationships with the guests and also very well about the service on board. Melisa always trying to do her best for the guests and their happiness very important for her. She likes to travelling , to learn different cultures and listening music. Speaks Turkish and high level English. "},{"name":"Nazli Demirci","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::4669f2f0-8e28-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nNazli is 45 years old and he has been working for many years with the quality yachts as house keeper and deck hand. She is looking forward to welcoming the guests onboard with his wonderful smile, applying his excellent organisational skills and offering the best service. Nazli will try to create for the guests an unforgettable cruising experience with her team! In her free time, he likes to watch movie and reading books. Speaks Turkish and middle level English."},{"name":"Alper Alparslan","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::602b4590-8e28-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nAlper is 23 years old and he has been working for 5 years with the quality yachts as stewardess and deck hand. He is graduated from Seamen high scholl in Bodrum. He is working with us more than 4 years and he is looking forward to welcoming the guests onboard with his wonderful smile, applying his excellent organisational skills and offering the best service. Alper will try to create for the guests an unforgettable cruising experience with his team! In his free time, he likes to watch movie and reading books. Speaks Turkish and middle level English "},{"name":"Ege Altındag","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::104ef900-c9a2-11ee-9ab2-a5f06501fa26::assets::77916a20-8e28-11f0-bcab-d985cb3d1cf0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Turkish\n\nEge is 23 years old and he has been working for 3 years with the quality yachts as intern sailor and deck hand. He is\nworking with us more than 2 years and he is still continue to university of seamen high school in Izmir. He is very keen\nabout the quests wishes and he wants to improve hisself in every part of seamanship. He likes to travelling and reading\nbook in his spare times. Speaks Turkish and beginner level English. "}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":5250000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":5250000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"May & October","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-05-01T00:00:0